Given	I'm logged-in with valid credentials
And	I'm on Page 06 of Hand MRI
When I select 'Finding' radio button
Then Finding dropdown menu is enabled

When I select 'Extensor tendons' from the dropdown menu
Then 'Add new finding' button is enabled
And 'Tendon abductor pollicis longus muscle' checkbox is enabled
And 'Tendon extensor pollicis brevis muscle' checkbox is enabled
And 'Tendon extensor carpi radialis longus muscle' checkbox is enabled
And 'Sehne M. extensor carpi radialis brevis' checkbox is enabled
And 'Tendon extensor pollicis longus muscle' checkbox is enabled
And 'Tendons extensores digitorum and indicis muscles' checkbox is enabled
And 'Tendon extensor digiti minimi muscle' checkbox is enabled
And 'Tendon extensor carpi ulnaris muscle' checkbox is enabled

And 'Tendinitis' radio button is enabled
And 'Tendovaginitis' radio button is enabled
And 'Rupture' radio button is enabled
And 'Peritendinous changes' checkbox is enabled


When I select 'Tendon abductor pollicis longus muscle' checkbox
Then 'Differential diagnosis' dropdown menu is enabled
When I select any diagnosis from 'Differential diagnosis' dropdown menu
Then 'Suspected' checkbox is enabled

When I select 'Tendon extensor pollicis brevis muscle' checkbox
Then 'Differential diagnosis' dropdown menu is enabled
When I select any diagnosis from 'Differential diagnosis' dropdown menu
Then 'Suspected' checkbox is enabled

When I select 'Tendon extensor pollicis longus muscle' checkbox
Then 'Differential diagnosis' dropdown menu is enabled
When I select any diagnosis from 'Differential diagnosis' dropdown menu
Then 'Suspected' checkbox is enabled

When I select 'Tendons extensores digitorum and indicis muscles' checkbox
Then 'D2' checkbox is enabled
And 'D3' checkbox is enabled
And 'D4' checkbox is enabled
And 'D5' checkbox is enabled

When I select 'Tendon extensor carpi ulnaris muscle' checkbox
Then 'Differential diagnosis' dropdown menu is enabled
When I select any diagnosis from 'Differential diagnosis' dropdown menu
Then 'Suspected' checkbox is enabled


When I select 'Tendinitis' radio button
Then 'With tendon tear' checkbox is enabled

When I select 'Tendovaginitis' radio button
Then 'Effusion in tendon sheath' radio button is enabled
And 'Chronic stenosing tendovaginitis' radio button is enabled
And 'Tendon sheath abscess' radio button is enabled
When I select 'Tendon sheath abscess' radio button
Then 'Max. size' input field is enabled

When I select 'Rupture' radio button
Then 'Partial rupture' radio button is enabled
And 'Complete rupture' radio button is enabled
When I select 'Complete rupture' radio button
Then 'Retraction' input field is enabled

When I select 'Peritendinous changes' checkbox
Then 'Peri-tenosynovitis' checkbox is enabled
And 'Tear at the enthesis' checkbox is enabled
And 'Perifocal hematoma' checkbox is enabled
